01:05:53.566 --> 01:05:56.168 line:90% position:50% align:center
He has led his people in the past.

01:05:56.168 --> 01:05:58.437 line:90% position:50% align:center
So when he prophesies

01:05:58.437 --> 01:06:00.873 line:90% position:50% align:center
